        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "Must the little ones, therefore, grow up in ignorance of the Word of God?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "This was impossible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "This was a wonderful proof of the Bible's living power.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "Now, however, it is believed that the Jews of Alexandria did the work entirely themselves, although their Greek Bible is still called the 'Septuagint'--that is, 'The Scriptures of the Seventy'--in memory of the old tradition.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "The Jews of old divided all dwellers on the earth into two classes: the Jews-that is, themselves; the Gentiles-that is, all the other nations.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "The Bible was now no longer locked up in a language which was already half forgotten.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "With this Greek translation its world-wide work had begun!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000033_000000",
