        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "The Jews accepted these Books as inspired; therefore the Samaritans rejected them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5217_24510_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5217/24510/5217_24510_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "Yet these hidden Samaritan documents, falsified as they had been, have had a work to do for God's Word within comparatively recent times.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
