        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5217",
        "content": "Not merely a different translation, remember, for the Bible should be the same in every language, but a Book of the Law in which some of the words had been changed and the original meaning destroyed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
